LogFile.FinalText: It is incredible how much they look alike. That is what a lot of people think about Denmark's two princesses. There are many similarities between Mary and Marie, but just as many dissimilarities, if not more. They are both from abroad, they are non-royal of birth and they have fallen in love with each their prince of Denmark. Mary is married to crown prince Frederik and Marie is married to prince Joachim. Also their names and appearances are incredibly similar. Both princesses are beautiful like models with long dark hair and big brown eyes. But despite their many similarities Mary and Marie are also two independent individuals, who have lived and still live their lives in their own way and this has molded their values and characters.
